# Hooks Directory Structure

The `src/hooks` directory contains custom React hooks for shared logic.

- [usePayment.ts](mdc:src/hooks/usePayment.ts): Custom hook for payment-related logic.
- [index.ts](mdc:src/hooks/index.ts): Main export or aggregation file for hooks.

## Usage

- Add new files here for additional custom hooks.
- Import and use hooks from this directory in your components.
